# sockets/
#
# WebSocket / Socket.IO event handlers (Phase 4).
#
# Planned namespaces:
#   /live  — real-time bus position stream
#   /eta   — ETA update push notifications
#
# Architecture note:
#   socket.js       — creates and configures the Socket.IO server
#   handlers/       — one file per event namespace
#   rooms.js        — room management (subscribe/unsubscribe by route)
